                Parvolus <lb n="2"/>hic situs est <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Ulp</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Iovinus <lb n="4"/>nomine qui vi<lb break="no" n="5"/>xit <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>os</ex></expan> V <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>enses</ex></expan> VI <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ies</ex></expan> XXIII hic solus <lb n="7"/>pater hunc hu<lb break="no" n="8"/>mav<supplied reason="lost">i</supplied>t parvolum <lb n="9"/>cuius de<supplied reason="lost">s</supplied>iderio <lb n="10"/>lumen intentus <lb n="11"/>dolet <expan><abbr>Ulp</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Vale<lb break="no" n="12"/>rianus b<expan><ex>ene</ex><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iciarius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ati</ex></expan> pa<lb break="no" n="13"/>ter a quo sibi <expan><abbr>sperab</abbr><ex>at</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>In drei Teile gebrochen und inzwischen verschollen; oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes Relief mit einem sitzenden Knaben.</p>
